<p style="margin:0 0 16px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;color:#3f4a3c;">Hi <%= @user.display_name %> 👋🏻</p>

<p style="margin:0 0 20px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;color:#3f4a3c;">
  You asked to export your Turf Monster wallet so you can take self-custody. Tap below to
  view your private key on a dedicated reveal page — the link expires in 30 minutes and can
  only be used once.
</p>

<table role="presentation" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" align="center" style="margin:0 auto;">
  <tr><td align="center" bgcolor="#4BAF50" style="border-radius:10px;">
    <a href="<%= @export_url %>" style="display:inline-block;padding:16px 40px;font-size:17px;font-weight:700;color:#ffffff;text-decoration:none;border-radius:10px;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;">Reveal my wallet keys →</a>
  </td></tr>
</table>

<p style="margin:28px 0 0;font-size:13px;line-height:1.5;color:#b91c1c;">
  <strong>Read this before clicking.</strong> Once your private key leaves Turf Monster, anyone who gets
  a copy can take everything in that wallet — and we can't recover it. Only continue on a private
  screen, ready to paste it into a wallet you trust.
</p>

<p style="margin:20px 0 0;font-size:12px;line-height:1.4;color:#8a948a;text-align:center;">
  Button not working? Copy and paste this link:<br>
  <a href="<%= @export_url %>" style="font-size:9px;line-height:1.3;color:#3d8b40;word-break:break-all;"><%= @export_url %></a>
</p>

<p style="margin:24px 0 0;font-size:13px;line-height:1.5;color:#6b756a;text-align:center;">
  Didn't request this? Ignore this email — your wallet stays custodial. Reach us at <%= @support_email %>.<br>— Turf Monster
</p>
